FBIS3-50298 "dreeu018_k_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-018 Document Type:Daily Report 27 Jan 1994 CROATIA U.S. Ambassador Visits UN Sector North LD2701095294 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in English 0903 GMT 27 Jan 94 LD2701095294 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The American ambassador to Croatia, Peter Galbraith, visited Topusko, Petrova Gora, and Glina in UN Sector North yesterday. A report from the American Embassy in Zagreb says that Mr. Galbraith wished to find out about the situation in that part of Croatian territory under UN protection. Mr. Galbraith described the visit as successful and said that it was important to start communicating.
